# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Ignore generated tensor and scaler files
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# PyTorch tensor binaries — several exceed GitHub's 100 MB file size limit.
# Regenerate by running:  python data_to_tensors.py
*.pt

# Fitted scikit-learn scalers — also reproducible via the pipeline.
*.pkl

# Keep this .gitignore itself tracked so the tensors/ directory is preserved
# in the repo as an intentional output location.
